post_text: The Tuttle Education Foundation is hosting a Spring Social at Remington Park in the Eclipse Suite on May 6, 6:00. We will have food, racing, silent auction, complementary bar the first hour, and FUN!!! All the proceeds will go back into the Tuttle Teachers' classrooms. Tickets are $65 each and there are a limited number of tickets available. This is for adults and the dress code is dressy casual. We will start selling tickets tomorrow morning at Preach's Total Fitness at 201 West Main and South Pointe Advertising at 301 West Main Street Suite B. Get your tickets before they are gone!!:).

text: Congratulations Mrs. Abello, Mrs. Atkins, and Mrs. Ferrell

post_text: Congratulations to our teachers of the year!!!Mrs. Abello is the Elementary School Teacher of the Year. Mrs. Ferrell is the Middle School Teacher of the Year. Mrs Atkins is the Intermediate School Teacher of the Year. Each teacher will be awarded a $400 grant from TEF to be used in their classrooms & TEF star to hang on their classroom door. Also, a big thank you to Oklahoma Cookie Jar for providing the cookies! Thank you Mr. Waitman & all the principals for allowing us time in the classroom to make presentations. We are so thankful for our teachers!!
